{"type":"message","id":"e31623e3","parentId":"ecbba638","timestamp":"2026-02-18T19:45:47.558Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[Wed 2026-02-18 21:45 GMT+2] OPERATION: ROADMAP V7.0 (COGNITIVE REVOLUTION).\n\n1.  **Architecture (Thinking Mode & MoE):**\n    *   *Docs:* Create `specs/THINKING_MODE.md`. Rule: Mandatory `<thinking>` block before ANY tool call.\n    *   *MoE:* Define roles in `docs/AGENTS_ROSTER.md` (Rust Engineer, Analyst, Risk Manager).\n\n2.  **HFT Dominance (Rust Supremacy):**\n    *   *Plan:* Rewrite `src/core/network.py` -> `src/rust_core/src/net.rs` (using `reqwest`).\n    *   *Tool:* `tui-dashboard` in Rust (`ratatui` crate).\n\n3.  **Self-Learning (Smart Search):**\n    *   *Skill:* `skills/smart-search.py`. Logic: Error -> Search -> Test -> Fix.\n\n4.  **Create ROADMAP V7:**\n    *   *File:* `docs/ROADMAP_V7.md`.\n    *   *Phase 4:* Cognitive (MoE + Thinking Mode).\n    *   *Phase 5:* HFT Supremacy (Rust Network + TUI).\n\n5.  **Output:**\n    *   Roadmap summary.\n    *   Thinking Mode benefits explanation."}],"timestamp":1771443947557}}
